        ### Getting to Todos Santos

        <img src="/images/info-to-be-known/space-shuttle.svg" height="300" class="gutter-image">

        ##### Flying In
        
        We recommend flying into San Jose del Cabo (about 1 hour, 15 minutes from Todos). Alternately, you can fly into La Paz (about ten minutes closer), but there are limited direct flights from the <abbr>US</abbr>. 

        ##### Rent a Car
        
        Although there are shuttles or taxis that can get you to Todos, a car is necessary to navigate from the town to the beach. Reserve your rental ahead of time because when you walk out of the airport, there will be 30+ car rental agents hassling for your business. When you exit the airport, look for the guy holding a sign for your rental company. I have used Cactus in the past. If you are only looking for transportation from the airport to Todos, [ecobajatours.com](http://ecobajatours.com/) offers $25 shuttles. They fill up though so book early. 

