        ##### Directions to Pachamama (wedding) 
        
      %ol.directions
        %li
          =image_tag 'images/info-to-be-known/directions/directions-hotel.svg'
          Take Topete out of town. You will pass Hotel Guaycura on your left.
        %li
          =image_tag 'images/info-to-be-known/directions/directions-left-turn.svg'
