        %li
          =image_tag 'images/info-to-be-known/directions/directions-left-turn.svg'
          Continue on the road until it becomes unpaved and then take your first left at Camino Viejo before the road dips down. Pachamama will be on your right side. Look for the white house and tepees. 

  
